{"tid":2311823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聶德權講大話 訛稱香港公務員均持有特區護照","createTime":"2020-12-04T11:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T11:08:29.000Z","uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd4aed6d24b26158912e4793b1a166f3b1ba847","tid":2311823,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:08:29.000Z","msg":"對於公務員宣誓效忠香港特區及中華人民共和國，是否不應同時持有外國國籍，聶德權說，《基本法》沒有要求公務員要放棄外國國籍，社會可以討論，但有關要求不在政府的議程。<strong><span class=\"red\">但他說，如果作為特區高級官員，往往會因履行公務代表特區出席國際場合，<span class=\"xx-large\">身份本身當然是持有特區護照</span>，這是很自然的事。</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563513-20201204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563513-20201204.htm&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=2ecf083d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563513-20201204.htm&h=862a8f65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563513-20201204.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n薪酬委員會指總薪級表34點或以上為高級公務員<br />\n但沒有法律規定高級公務員必須為中國國籍人士<br />\n他們可以為外國籍永久居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/popo-04_g1VsA_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpopo-04_g1VsA_1200x0.png&h=54f485c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莊定賢做PTU校長時去外國交流用咩護照？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警隊成日又美國又新加坡<br />\n好想政府交代下用「有冇外國護照持有人代表香港作官方訪問」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係要美國政府代為解答？"}]}